Harrys My Free Farm Bash Bot (MFF Bash Bot)
-------------------------------------------

README_EN
---------

I am very sorry for not releasing this bot in english language.
As you may be able to tell from the code, i was going to translate all
of it, but pulled back from the workload since i did't want to release
it to the public at that time.

If you want to contribute or create your own version... be my guest :)

If you don't care too much for the GUI (it's entirely in german), you can get
the bot part to work anyway. Try and hurl the INSTALL file through google
translate. You may also need to adjust the bot script. Good luck.
